{
  "stem": "25938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not clear to me, but I remember vaguely all the-- all these things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard about--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About-- I don't remember about-- I don't remember of any Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was another place called, [INAUDIBLE], we-- we read about that-- that-- a-- a place, a-- a death camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We read about this place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew it would be-- we would be going to-- to-- to be killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew something that would end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We expected end.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People said, you know, said the-- Widduy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, Yiddish Widduy that before you die, you confess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There is a Jewish confession called Widduy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the other people said in-- in the train, I remember, they said this Widduy, this prayer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We just-- [INAUDIBLE] a way to-- to escape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So in Birkenau, we were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't announce.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- I don't-- no, I can't answer that question.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came there, and that-- that was Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was Birkenau, Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we came there, [INAUDIBLE] many people, many hundreds, thousands of people talked about Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That we called it Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Big, huge houses, barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People lived there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- I see nothing except the-- this-- this-- the Auschwitz where the-- the people were-- were-- were living there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I-- I went-- I went to a few selections.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to-- to-- to work around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mengele used to stand near us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Naked, we used to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to see if someone is very, very thin, they used to send to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the first few selections, it was all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The last selection, I remember, he-- he picked my-- my number.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He sent me to the crematory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to the--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just the finger.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He put--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
